{"tid":213212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大角咀女子遭淋鏹毀容　警拘涉案狠婦","createTime":"2017-04-23T03:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T10:19:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b102d6757d0b230930e8cdfa2b6706e50ba7424","tid":213212,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170423/large/1492913713_793b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170423%2Flarge%2F1492913713_793b.jpg&h=b0a2d3de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上9時許，大角嘴通州街178號富安大廈樓上一單位，一名35歲女子遭人向面部淋疑是鏹水的液體，當場昏迷。警員接報趕到，拘捕一名涉案女子，她面部及手腳受傷，其中面部似乎亦被腐液濺中，須要送院。而女事主面部受創，送院時赤腳，被包上保鮮紙，擔架床滿是血迹，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，女事主搬到上址劏房不久。被捕疑犯今早登門找晦氣，雙方為金錢問題爭執。其間有人亮刀，並向女事主淋潑疑為鏹水的液體。女事主臉部及身體受創，昏迷送院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n街坊透露，事發後女疑犯曾拍門向鄰房單位的婆婆求助，以普通話說：「殺咗人，幫忙報警。」惟婆婆可能聽不懂，另一名男街坊聞聲了解後，即協助報警。"},{"pid":"3b4f504fe7d59eb28771c00c6853dd68e868e40c","tid":213212,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56601417&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56601417%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170423&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=cc289db2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56601417%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170423&h=6f6feb4d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56601417&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170423</a>"},{"pid":"88cc52a14a413599f2cc9735f576e5bfcbeebf6a","tid":213212,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"蝗 vs 蝗